      * Driver di stampa   PDF - Versione 1.3                          *
      *                                                                *
      *                    Gestisce i formati : A4                     *
      *                    ------------------------------------------- *
      *                     Versione originale:    001 del 01/04/02    *
      *                       Ultima revisione:    NdK del 05/04/02    *
      *                    ------------------------------------------- *
      *                                 Autore:    Nicola de Kunovich  *
      * -------------------------------------------------------------- *
      *                                                                *
      * Compatibile Acrobat Versioni 4.0.x, 5.0.x                      *
      *                                                                *
      * -------------------------------------------------------------- *
      *                                                                *
      * Canale di uscita specifico : ucp */abd/asc/@/pdf/out/*&        *
      *                                                                *
      *  - '@' : Inserimento del codice utente Tangram nel pathname    *
      *          (Opzionale)                                           *
      *  - '&' : Inserimento del suffisso '.pdf' nel pathname          *
      *          (Obbligatorio)                                        *
      *                                                                *
      * -------------------------------------------------------------- *
      *                                                                *
      * Vedi parametri per driver 'psua4' - PostScript                 *
      *                                                                *
      *================================================================*

      ******************************************************************
       Environment Division.
      ******************************************************************

      *================================================================*
       Configuration Section.
      *================================================================*

       Source-Computer.     w-i-p-NdK-PD .
       Object-Computer.     w-i-p-NdK-PD .

       Special-Names.       Decimal-Point is comma .

      *================================================================*
       Input-Output Section.
      *================================================================*

       File-Control.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * File Control [bin]                                        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           select bin        assign       to input-output   f-bin-pat
                             organization is binary sequential
                             access  mode is sequential
                             file  status is                f-bin-sts .

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * File Control [b01], per il trattamento di [bin]           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           select b01        assign       to input-output   f-b01-pat
                             organization is binary sequential
                             access  mode is sequential
                             file  status is                f-b01-sts .

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * File Control [b02], per il trattamento di [bin]           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           select b02        assign       to input-output   f-b02-pat
                             organization is binary sequential
                             access  mode is sequential
                             file  status is                f-b02-sts .

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * File Control [pss]                                        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           select  optional  pss   assign to disk         f-pss-pat
                             organization is indexed
                             access mode  is dynamic
                             record key   is pss-key
                             file status  is f-pss-sts                .

