      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-fil-bin-wrt-rec      .
           string    w-fce-rrq  delimited by   spaces
                     " "        delimited by   size
                     w-fce-tix  delimited by   spaces
                     " l"       delimited by   size
                     w-c0c-CR   delimited by   size
                                          into w-fil-bin-wrt-rec      .
