           move      02                   to   w-fil-bin-wrt-lun      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Incremento contatore byte                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       w-fil-bin-wrt-lun    to   w-pdf-ctr-byt          .
